@startuml component-main-service
'' ============================================================================
'' vinary-viewer — Component view of the MAIN process (core + service)
''
'' PlantUML over Mermaid because: we mix *concrete* components (slate) with
'' «planned» ones (dashed grey stereotype) in one diagram, plus an amber band of
'' ipcMain handlers that bridge to the renderer. PlantUML's `component<<planned>>`
'' skinparam (defined in _vv-theme.iuml) makes Forthcoming ports visually obvious;
'' Mermaid has no per-node stereotype styling.
'' ============================================================================
!include _vv-theme.iuml

title MAIN process — components (`vinary.main.*`)  ·  dashed = Forthcoming

skinparam component {
  BorderThickness 1.5
}

component "vinary.main.core" as Core MAIN_COLOR {
}
note bottom of Core
  `main` — app bootstrap
  `create-window!` — BrowserWindow
    (contextIsolation, preload)
  `initial-file` — parse argv
end note

component "vinary.main.service" as Svc MAIN_COLOR
note bottom of Svc
  `kind-of` — md / image / text
  `send-content!` — read + push
  `repo-tree` / `send-tree!` — git
  `open!` / `close!` — chokidar watch
  `init!` — register ipcMain handlers
end note

component "ipcMain handlers" as Ipc IPC_COLOR {
  portin "vv:open" as POpen
  portin "vv:close" as PClose
}

cloud "Node built-ins\n(fs · path · child_process)" as Node FS_COLOR
cloud "chokidar\n(per-path watcher)" as Chk FS_COLOR
cloud "git CLI\n(rev-parse · ls-files)" as Git FS_COLOR

component "preload\ncontextBridge `window.vv`" as Preload IPC_COLOR

'' ---- Forthcoming ports (planned, not built) ----
component "PDF port\n(BrowserView)" as Pdf <<planned>>
component "Diagram port\n(d2 / plantuml / mermaid → SVG)" as Dia <<planned>>
component "Grammar registry\n(~/.config/vinary-viewer)" as Reg <<planned>>

Core --> Svc          : `service/init!`,\n`service/open!`
Core --> Preload      : `webPreferences.preload`
Svc  --> Node         : read file · dirname
Svc  --> Chk          : watch open path
Svc  --> Git          : repo tree
Svc  --> Ipc          : `init!` registers
POpen --> Svc         : `open!` (read + watch)
PClose --> Svc        : `close!` (stop watcher)
Svc ..> Preload       : `webContents.send`\n(amber: vv:content / vv:error / vv:tree)

Svc ..> Pdf  : «planned»
Svc ..> Dia  : «planned»
Svc ..> Reg  : «planned»

legend right
  |= Colour |= Concept |
  | <#3A5BA0> | MAIN / Node IO component |
  | <#B1951D> | IPC seam (ipcMain / preload) |
  | <#9F8766> | external resource (fs · git · chokidar) |
  | <#DDDDDD> | Forthcoming (planned, dashed) |
endlegend
@enduml
